## ğŸ”§ Customization

### Adding New Page Objects

1. Create new page class extending `BasePage`
2. Define platform-specific locators using `@AndroidFindBy` and `@iOSXCUITFindBy`
3. Implement page-specific methods

```java
public class NewPage extends BasePage {
    @AndroidFindBy(id = "android.id")
    @iOSXCUITFindBy(accessibility = "ios.accessibility.id")
    private WebElement element;
    
    // Page methods here
}
```

### Adding New Test Cases

1. Create test class extending `BaseTest`
2. Use TestNG annotations for test configuration
3. Implement data-driven testing with `@DataProvider`

```java
public class NewTests extends BaseTest {
    @Test(dataProvider = "testData")
    public void testMethod(String param1, String param2) {
        // Test implementation
    }
}
```

